Package: cellpanelr
Title: Analyze Data from Cell Line Panels
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = c("Douglas", "R"),
           family = "Wassarman",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dwassar@gmail.com")
Description: A Shiny app and R package for analyzing response data collected
  from panels of cell lines. It uses data sets and annotations publicly
  available from [DepMap](<https://depmap.org/portal/>) to identify features that
  correlate with user-provided data.
